  "description": "Now that Fornaxos has freed her of her ancestor's vow, Antares finds herself fascinated by the many peoples and cultures of Erden. Like a firefly on the breeze, she flits from place to place, learning all she can.\n\nAs a former recluse, however, she never had to learn to tame the considerable fire magic within her. This has caused its fair share of difficulties in her travels. For instance, one bikki village forbade her to return after she dried up all its mud baths in a single day.\n\nIf you know any tutors of fire magic that don't mind getting a few burns, please let her know.",
